prompts.frontCover:
Front cover of a minimalist and humorous birthday greeting card. A flat 2D vector illustration of the people from the reference photo, Lao Lao and Jordan, styled as simple, clean cartoon characters.

The scene depicts Jordan playfully trying to lift Lao Lao, who is laughing joyfully. Jordan is shown with a slight, exaggerated bend in his knees and a comical straining expression on his face, as if Lao Lao is surprisingly heavy, while Lao Lao looks delighted and carefree, kicking one leg up in the air. Lao Lao is wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt and Jordan is wearing a tan hoodie, mirroring their clothing in the photo.

The background is a solid, soft pastel color like mint green or pale yellow, ensuring the focus is on the characters. Below the characters, a few simple, whimsical birthday elements are scattered, such as tiny floating confetti pieces or a single, elegantly drawn party popper icon.

In the center of the card, placed safely above the characters, the greeting text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script in a dark charcoal color. The overall composition is clean, modern, and lighthearted.
